title: ddfprod 893vsv - Sandra Shine & Samantha
description:
Sandy's Fantasies (sandysfantasies.com) by ddfprod (Denys Defrancesco) - series 893vsv - Sandra Shine and Samantha. 

Sandy's Fantasies used to be one of ddfprod's websites, hosted by the beautiful lesbian(?) model Sandy (or Zsanett Egerhazi as she's known in Budapest, Hungary). The site features also lots of photoshoots with Sophie Moone (aka Sophie Sweet in some sites). Today the site is still there, but it's been a while since they updated it.
